title: Why Canada, NOT BLUE AMERICA, Pushed Back on COVID Mandates | Louder with Crowder
description: Canadians are revolting, and Justin Trudeau stinks on ice! We tell you what you need to know about the Freedom Convoy of truckers protesting mandates. We also tackle the Joe Rogan/Spotify controversy. And actor Michael Rapaport almost realizes the consequences of voting for Dems. #JoeRogan #Spotify #FreedomConvoy
